Install NodeJS from below Site
  https://nodejs.org/en

Install angular CLI globally
  npm install -g @angular/cli@17
  
Create a new Angular application Standalone
  ng new <Application Name>

Create a new Angular application without Standalone
  ng new my-app --no-standalone --routing --ssr=false

Add Material Dependency to the Application
  ng add @angular/material

Create Environment Folder on to the Application
  ng g environments
